{"id":371929,"date":[{"year":1958,"month":7,"day":3}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"159","ytitle":"","mtitle":"新儿歌三首","ftitle":"","authors":["放明"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"放明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好铁才打钉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好儿才当兵；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好铁打钉修大门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好儿当兵守大陈(注)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注:大陈是指海防前线瓯江口外的大陈岛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸上工厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈上工场；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸上工厂去打钉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈上工场去打绳；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修条船来织张网，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捕来鱼儿“满登登”。(注)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注:“满登登”是温州方言，是多的意思。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大哥造水库，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二哥挖河泥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姊挑垃圾我积肥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说亩产千斤不容易?"}]}